\par }{\f4 
When you have played exactly 700 miles (you cannot go over) the computer will ask if you wish to extend the game to 1000 miles.  If you answer No, you will win the game. If you answer Yes, you must play to exactly 1000 miles before you win the game (and t
}{\f4 he computer might just beat you to it).  Winning the game on an Extension will add 200 points to your score.  }{\f4 
\par }{\f4 \page }{\fs16\up6 #{\footnote \pard\plain \s245 \f3\fs20\lang1033 {\fs16\up6 #} endgame}}{\fs16\up6  ${\footnote \pard\plain \s245 \f3\fs20\lang1033 {\fs16\up6 $} End of game}}{\fs16\up6  +{\footnote \pard\plain \s245 \f3\fs20\lang1033 {\fs16\up6 +}
